- # ================= profile ユーザー詳細ページ ===============
.col-md-8.border-profile
  .d-flex
    div
      = link_to "/" do
        i.fa-solid.fa-arrow-left.arrow-left
    .profile-top-name
      h2
        = current_user.name
      p
        | 320 posts
  .profile-images
    - if @user.header.attached?
      = image_tag current_user.header, class: "header-img", alt: "..."
    - else
      img.header-img[src="/assets/header.jpg"]
    - if @user.icon.attached?
      = image_tag current_user.icon, class: "profile-img me-3", alt: "..."
    - else
      img.profile-img.me-3[src="/assets/icon.png"]
    - if current_user
      = link_to "Edit profile", edit_user_path(@user) , class: "edit"
  .profile-info
    h2
      = current_user.name
    p
      | @
      = current_user.username
    - if current_user.self_introduction.present?
      p
        = current_user.self_introduction
    - else
      p.dammy_self_introduction
        | (参考例 自己紹介文を登録したら消えます) 千葉県在住。25歳。23/3~8/8まで独学(500h)。23/8/9~HC。英語も学習中。ゴルフ、筋トレ、ランニング、ママさんバレー、料理、ヨガ、瞑想、将棋、カラオケ、登山です。よろしくお願いします！
    .d-flex
      .profile-details
        i.fa-solid.fa-location-dot.profile-icon-link
        span
          = current_user.location
      .profile-details
        i.fa-solid.fa-link.profile-icon-link
        span
          = current_user.website
      .profile-details
        i.fa-solid.fa-cake-candles.profile-icon
        span
          = current_user.date_of_birth.strftime('%Y年%m月%d日')
    .profile-details.calender-icon
      i.fa-regular.fa-calendar-days.profile-icon
      span
        = current_user.created_at.strftime('%Y年%m月')
        | からColorful SNSを利用しています
    .d-flex.relationship
      .follow
        p
          span
            | 80
          |  Following
      .follow
        p
          span
            | 80
          |  Followers
